   but many of his competitors  
         are struggling         

438
00:27:32,368 --> 00:27:36,486
       to eke out a living      
  as the fish fail to rebound.  

439
00:27:36,488 --> 00:27:38,372
        And a lolot of guys     
     didn't get through it.     

440
