     about other fishermen.     

451
00:28:16,278 --> 00:28:19,613
At a meeting where a proposal to
 provide emergency-relief money 

452
00:28:19,615 --> 00:28:22,249
     to suffering fishermen     
          is discussed,         

453
00:28:22,251 --> 00:28:24,451
        Rafael speaks up.       

454
00:28:24,453 --> 00:28:25,753
      Kendall: Carlos said,     
