457
00:28:29,542 --> 00:28:32,543
        I mean, that was        
        Carlos' opinion.        

458
00:28:32,545 --> 00:28:35,596
 There was a young man who said 
    that he wanted to be able   

459
00:28:35,598 --> 00:28:39,016
      to get into fishing,      
   and Carlos said, you know,   

460
00:28:39,018 --> 00:28:41,435
       "This guy is never       
     gonna get into fishing.    

461
00:28:41,437 --> 00:28:43,754
      I am gonna squash him     
