506
00:31:02,161 --> 00:31:04,695
     And so you had to stop     
          right there.          

507
00:31:04,697 --> 00:31:07,197
   Narrator: And, inevitably,   
         some fishermen         

508
00:31:07,199 --> 00:31:10,033
   do not have enough permits   
      to stay in business.      

509
00:31:10,035 --> 00:31:14,371
 And, once again, Carlos Rafael 
   is there to buy their boats  

510
00:31:14,373 --> 00:31:18,208
       and their permits,       
  ostensibly bailing them out,  

511
00:31:18,210 --> 00:31:21,762
