     his personal ambition.     

512
00:31:39,932 --> 00:31:44,151
   This may be Rafael's moment  
      to get total control.     

513
00:31:44,153 --> 00:31:48,922
    But that does not mean he   
 will stop also trying to steal.

514
00:31:48,924 --> 00:31:50,724
        In October 2013,        

515
00:31:50,726 --> 00:31:56,496
one of his boats reports a catch
