518
00:32:05,290 --> 00:32:08,225
 over six times what he reports.

519
00:32:08,227 --> 00:32:15,182
     He gets caught, again,     
   and NOAA fines him $70,000.  

520
00:32:15,184 --> 00:32:17,601
  Rafael can afford that fine,  

521
00:32:17,603 --> 00:32:19,486
      and so he is willing      
          to take risks         

522
00:32:19,488 --> 00:32:22,856
      that other fishermen      
      would not dare take.      

523
00:32:22,858 --> 00:32:25,809
  Sykes: I'd be scared to death 
         that they'd...         

524
00:32:25,811 --> 00:32:27,611
    He had a lot of permits,    

525
00:32:27,613 --> 00:32:29,613
    so maybe he could afford    
       to lose one or two.      

