00:32:29,615 --> 00:32:31,198
          I've got one.         

527
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:33,533
         If I lose that,        
    a boat without permits --   

528
00:32:33,535 --> 00:32:36,820
     not totally worthless,     
       but not worth much.      

529
00:32:36,822 --> 00:32:39,289
     Lelling: They're trying    
      to follow the rules.      

530
00:32:39,291 --> 00:32:44,127
    They're trying to eke out   
a living with maybe three boats.

531
00:32:44,129 --> 00:32:47,381
   Here you have Carlos Rafael  
