904
00:59:04,925 --> 00:59:07,059
        and the fact that       
     he had been prosecuted     

905
00:59:07,061 --> 00:59:08,677
     three times in the past    

906
00:59:08,679 --> 00:59:12,931
       for crimes related       
    to his fishing business.    

907
00:59:12,933 --> 00:59:16,051
     So I think we were able    
   to convince the court that,  

908
00:59:16,053 --> 00:59:19,938
 unless federal law-enforcement 
  was gonna be a complete joke, 

909
00:59:19,940 --> 00:59:23,358
   it had to be the last time.  

910
00:59:23,360 --> 00:59:26,028
                     ♪♪         

911
00:59:26,030 --> 00:59:28,396
        Narrator: Rafael        
