913
00:59:30,701 --> 00:59:33,118
      that his crimes have      
       hurt the reputation      

914
00:59:33,120 --> 00:59:35,070
     of all fishermen here,     

915
00:59:35,072 --> 00:59:39,174
     who essentially operate    
       in an honor system.      

916
00:59:39,176 --> 00:59:41,960
   Shelley: Carlos didn't care  
