917
00:59:41,962 --> 00:59:47,799
       In fact, he used it      
        to his advantage,       

918
00:59:47,801 --> 00:59:49,801
  and, really, in the process,  

919
00:59:49,803 --> 00:59:52,971
     dishonored every other     
      law-abiding fisherman     

920
00:59:52,973 --> 00:59:55,307
        out on the water.       

921
00:59:55,309 --> 00:59:58,043
       Narrator: And those      
      law-abiding fishermen     

922
00:59:58,045 --> 01:00:00,646
     believe that is unfair.    

923
01:00:00,648 --> 01:00:02,064
 They have a message for anyone 

924
01:00:02,066 --> 01:00:05,600
       who hears the story      
        of Carlos Rafael.       

